description: Returns the list of votes for a specified proposal, including the value of each vote and the unique identifier of the member that cast the vote. Applies only to Hyperledger Fabric.

parameters.name: NetworkId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the network.

parameters.name: ProposalId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the proposal.

nested_items.name: Vote
nested_items.description: The vote value, either YES or NO.

nested_items.name: MemberName
nested_items.description: The name of the member that cast the vote.

nested_items.name: MemberId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the member that cast the vote.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that indicates the next set of results to retrieve.
